              "display_title": "Pahrak-Kal",
              "description": "Pahrak-Kal is a slow-moving powerhouse. Although it would seem this Bohrok-Kal would be easy to evade, that is not so. The Pahrak-Kal is a juggernaut that can plough through any obstacle on the way to its goal. Anything it cannot break through, it can melt with its amazing plasma shield.",
